The '''Yellow-barred Heliconian''' was a species of [[Butterfly/Legends|butterfly]]. It had pale yellow wings with white trim and a broken white bar across the middle. An example of this specimen was found at the [[Garden of Butterflies]] on [[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]].<ref name="marvel48">[[Star Wars (1977) 48|''Star Wars'' (1977) 48]]</ref>

